capasm (1.0.0) focal; urgency=medium

  * bug fixes
  * much refactoring 
  * new ncas assembler
  * capasm: suppress superfluous code output of BSZ pseudo-ops
  * capasm: extended check marks redefinition of global symbols if there is a type or value mismatch
  * capasm: fix incorrect range checks of relative jumps
  * capasm: suppress superfluous code output of BSZ pseudo-ops
  * capasm: line numbers in list file
  * capasm: parsing of conditional assembly pseudo-ops fixed


 -- bionic <achim@trillian>  Tue, 08 Dec 2020 19:14:06 +0100

capasm (0.9.8) bionic; urgency=medium

  * added support for ASP/ASP statements with numeric length qualifiers
  * removed "'" as alternate string delimiter 
  * removed -m option, added -q option and enhanced global symbols capabilities
  * allow more special characters in symbol names
  * refactoring
  * added capconv tool

 -- bionic <achim@trillian>  Thu, 23 Jul 2020 17:16:08 +0200

capasm (0.9.7) bionic; urgency=medium

  * added HP-75 rom support to caprom
  * added support for hex and bin constants
  * added support for non octal register numbers
  * added LOC and HED pseudo ops
  * literal data list error fixes 

 -- bionic <achim@trillian>  Tue, 21 Jul 2020 16:04:25 +0200

capasm (0.9.6) bionic; urgency=medium

  * added HP-87 compatible NAM statement
  * added conditional assembly pseudo ops
  * added relative GTO
  * added include and link file support
  * added caprom tool
  * added hex output of addresses and program code in list file
  * bug fixes
  * refactoring

